Air Berlin May Cut Job Cuts, Financial Times Deutschland Says

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-09-01T18:57:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-01/air-berlin-may-cut-job-cuts-financial-times-deutschland-says.html
Air Berlin Plc (AB1)  doesn’t rule out job
cuts as it evaluates its business model, including its airport
network and fleet,  Financial Times Deutschland  reported in a
preview of an article that will be published tomorrow, citing a
letter from Air Berlin’s management to the company’s employees.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
